import {Routes, Router} from 'react-router-dom'
import {AnimalList, AnimalDetail, Search, PageNotFound} from "../pages"

import React from 'react'

export const AllRoutes = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<AnimalList />}/>
        <Route path="/category/dogs" element={<AnimalList />}/>
        <Route path="/category/cats" element={<AnimalList />}/>
        <Route path="/category/birds" element={<AnimalList />}/>
        <Route path="/search" element={<Search />}/>
        <Route path="*" element={<PageNotFound />}/>

    </Routes>
    </>
  )
}
